item.title: CVE-2023-28370|2023-05-25T00:00:00 -- tornadoweb -- tornado
item.description: Open redirect vulnerability in Tornado versions 6.3.1 and earlier allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to redirect a user to an arbitrary web site and conduct a phishing attack by having user access a specially crafted URL.
